725589f-c.title: Queens: 69th Street - Juniper Valley Road
725589f-c.text:
69th Street, east side, north froa and across Juniper
Valley Road, showing (left) the Ferguson House, built
about 1840, and the former District School No. 6 (right),
the latter being at the N. E. corner of Juniper Valley
Road. 69th Street, here, was formely naamed Juniper Avenue.
Views 1,2,3: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection View 1: 1922
MAY BE REPRODUCED  Views 2,3: 1923
View 4: P. L. Sperr  July 2, 1935
NO REPRODUCTIONS
